Peninsula 1, St Tropez
A popular place for parties, Peninsula 1 is a spacious property with ample outdoor space and some unusual features. Although the pool is a popular amenity, it features a mobile base which can be elevated to turn the entire area into a large terrace.
Sleeps: Nne in four bedrooms
Costs: From €22,500 per week
